cdata.name: Lightpaycoin
cdata.desc:
Lightpaycoin is a blockchain-based payment network. LPCs goal is to build & supply user-friendly PoS (Point of Sale) devices, design ATMs that receive NFC (Near Field Communication) technology and ease the use of LPC wallets.

The Lightpaycoin native asset is LPC, and it is mineable. The LPC will be a medium of exchange, store of value within the Lightpaycoin ecosystem.
